Description: Reproducibility package for the paper "General Frameworks for
    Conditional Two-Sample Testing" (Lee, Cha, and Kim, 2024). Implements
    Algorithm 1 (subsampling-based reduction of conditional two-sample
    testing to conditional independence testing) together with the
    density-ratio-based and conditional-kernel test families used as
    baselines. Reproduces all main-paper figures and appendix results.
URL: https://github.com/suman-cha/Cond2ST,
    https://arxiv.org/abs/2410.16636
BugReports: https://github.com/suman-cha/Cond2ST/issues
